results.description:
THE FINALE TO THE FIRST VOLUME OF S.H.I.E.L.D.!
This chapter comes to a close in a fashion that will have your jaw on the floor. It is Da Vinci vs. Newton with the fate of the world in the balance. Who is the Night Machine on the side of? What role will the Celestial Child play? The most talked about book of 2010 closes its first volume with a bang. But donâ€™t worry, the same team will be back soon with volume 2!
